description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 Min CALISTHENICS UPPER BODY WORKOUT at Home | No Equipment' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow along to build muscle and strength with this 15 minute upper body Calisthenics workout. You can do this bodyweight workout at home with no equipment. This strength routine includes the best bodyweight Calisthenics exercises for optimal results.

Beginner variations are included in this video alongside intermediate / advanced options making it suitable for everyone to enhance their Calisthenics training.
